{"tid":1682650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最新風向：唔好用標題吸引注意","createTime":"2019-10-30T07:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T12:48:01.000Z","uid":202464,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d533189d93e7453c2c99ff2bcc4d989126de535d","tid":1682650,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:35:16.000Z","msg":"「文不對題」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nE.G. <br />\n標題：「香港輸緊，我教你知要點做。」<br />\n<br />\n內容：星期六上街，光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完全係「狼來了」，久而久之就沒有人再相信轟動的標題。"},{"pid":"6ee181f87c5db08441c0dd42e16adf8f09e710d7","tid":1682650,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:35:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPMCZAr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPMCZAr.jpg&h=a189dd43&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1fb2e7c4d41255235eda619e47f5f4dc80d774f3","tid":1682650,"uid":256246,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:37:12.000Z","msg":"好明顯果d都係五毛，就係等果d唔會個個topic襟入去睇果d人中招跟住帶風向"},{"pid":"cccdfead407dfdcd49626bfbecff6b50bf2cf05f","tid":1682650,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6ee181f87c5db08441c0dd42e16adf8f09e710d7","tid":1682650,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:35:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPMCZAr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPMCZAr.jpg&h=a189dd43&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:37:47.000Z","msg":"每篇帖文的第一、二個回覆，必然是用bot自動留言。<br />\n<br />\n洗版「行動留言」，等於每天經過的廣告牌，它愈出現在你眼皮底下，你愈習慣去忽視它。<br />\n<br />\n你不忽視「行動留言」就沒有辦法認真閱讀該帖，因為它總是隔在帖文與留言之間。<br />\n<br />\n正常的讀者看完帖文後必然是立刻拉下去看留言回覆，若然看到與主題無關的「行動留言」，就會自動忽略的，久而久之就會訓練忽略的習慣。"},{"pid":"975472c0e2a850f92285169867220013f73061be","tid":1682650,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"多謝警隊接受本人嘅建議，今日在通訊軟件收到一條消息：<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>現時應是四大協會一起召集開全體會員大會，<span style=\"color: red;\">敦促政府表態全力</span>，全方位支持警隊平暴，由六月十二日宣佈暴動那天開始，警隊進入平暴止亂的階段，一切有関投訴警隊的使用武力，法律程序，拘捕手段和所謂冇禮貌等，一慨不被接納！<br />\n政府堅定向社會表明不會有任何所謂棄車保帥，通過檢控和犧牲部份警員，來換取暴亂派停止暴亂行為，堅決不會和任何暴亂派有談判和交易以保障所有為保衛香港的警隊成員不會被出賣。💪💪💪👊👊👊<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>警</strong>得罪中央犯死罪</span>，三萬科士<span style=\"color: red;\">大禍臨頭</span>！<br />\n+ <span style=\"color: gold;\">送條妙計<strong>俾阿Sir解圍</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1671833\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1671833</a>"},{"pid":"2da726b6dce2a7def85ca3d7cbb1ba4371fc5b37","tid":1682650,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871712fa7c6f6fc53a4321401be45c9fd0aae890","tid":1682650,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a42e51d4f0bb900c322dce0b2e9269d9a17d24","tid":1682650,"uid":171278,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b8818173f55b01b05faf89522ff257055d2c3e","tid":1682650,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e6a42e51d4f0bb900c322dce0b2e9269d9a17d24","tid":1682650,"uid":171278,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:50:05.000Z","msg":"一鬧佢地就話「不分化」、然後就話你「五毛」。<br />\n<br />\n我相信班標題黨係有心玩野"},{"pid":"2b9e5a1b65d0ad5f9e7544b33824000a4a925818","tid":1682650,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:53:28.000Z","msg":"呢個真係要檢討 其實好多廢中(包括我)都開始上 唔好再成日標題黨"},{"pid":"eb80c4e3656e470870ea1ca06605cc62c2322e46","tid":168265